The '''Old South Road''', also referred to as just the '''South Road''', was an ancient roadway from [[Tol Sirion]] heading south through the [[Crossings of Taeglin]] and passing along the western edge of the [[Moors of the Nibin-noeg]] before reaching [[Nargothrond]].<ref>{{CH|Map}}</ref><ref>{{CH|6}}, p. 109</ref> 
